  "title": "Tapping for 3am thought loops",
  "subtitle": "A five-minute script for stepping out of the mental spin.",
  "excerpt": "A five-minute tapping practice from Day 14 of the SLEEP program. The script targets the thought loop: the mind that rehearses conversations, plans problems that don't exist yet, and uses repetition as a substitute for safety.",
  "type": "PRACTICE",
  "sourceNotes": "Adapted from Day 14 of SLEEP: A 30-Day Tapping Intensive to Fall Asleep Faster and Wake Energised (Rebecca J Page, 2025, ISBN 9798269649795), \"Unwind Mental Loops.\" Tapping framework: Gary Craig's Emotional Freedom Technique (EFT), in use since the mid-1990s, building on Roger Callahan's Thought Field Therapy.",
  "body": {
